      "filePath": "iac/provider-aws/init/outputs.tf",
      "summary": "Terraform 输出定义，导出 S3 存储桶名称、ECR 仓库名称、Cloudflare 配置以及 VPC、子网和安全组 ID 等关键基础设施标识，供下游模块引用。",
      "tags": ["infrastructure", "terraform", "outputs", "configuration"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
